; Coverage test for filters.cc lines 1070-1071
; Tests interval_posts::operator() without a duration (no --weekly/--monthly)
; but with a period range that uses find_period to filter posts.
; Lines 1070-1071: the else-if branch when interval has no duration
; but find_period succeeds, forwarding the post directly.

2024/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food             $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/20 Restaurant
    Expenses:Dining           $75.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/04/10 Outside Range
    Expenses:Other            $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --period "from 2024/01/01 to 2024/03/01"
24-Jan-15 Groceries             Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-50.00            0
24-Feb-20 Restaurant            Expenses:Dining              $75.00       $75.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-75.00            0
end test
